title: Fixed a bug with how I created the HttpsConnector.
message:
Fixed a bug with how I created the HttpsConnector.
I was creating it too early, before the username and password were entered.
This caused the connector to have a user and psss of "" and therefore it would never work until you closed the app and opened it again
without logging out and back in.
